<div class="card card-var">
  <h3>Why Do We Need More Than the Mean?</h3>
  <p>Two datasets can have the <strong>exact same mean</strong> but look completely different! We need to measure how <strong>spread out</strong> the data is.</p>

  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin:20px 0;">
